<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-06-20 02:28 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A2547 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u s &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-HKN-NHLNOTEBOOK-BOS &LR;      06-20 1888
