<P>
   FANFAIR-NASHVILLE (Nashville) _ Something was different at Fan
Fair this year. There was no Garth and no Shania Twain or Dixie
Chicks or Reba McIntyre. Some country music stars, fans grumbled,
are getting too swell-headed for their cowboy hats. By Neil
Strauss.
</P>
<P>
   TOBACCO-ENTERTAINMENT (Undated) _ While tobacco companies have
agreed to phase out their sponsorship of sporting events, they seem
to have no trouble putting their names on entertainment events. By
Peter Applebome.
</P>
