TREASURY TO OFFER BILLS AND A NOTE THIS WEEK 
</HEADLINE>
  (lb) 
 c.1999 N.Y. Times News Service   
<TEXT>
<P>
   The Treasury's schedule of financing this week offers Monday's
weekly auction of new three- and six-month bills, and auctions of
52-week bills and a two-year note on Tuesday and Wednesday,
respectively.
</P>
